data.title: Bitmine Immersion (BMNR) Buys 14,618 ETH Amid Rising Institutional Interest
data.description: Bitmine Immersion Technologies (NYSE American: BMNR) acquired an additional 14,618 ETH on Friday, according to on-chain data platforms. Fundstrat’s Tom Lee-backed Ethereum treasury firm continues to buy the dip amid a revival in Ethereum interest among institutional investors. Bitmine Immersion Bags 14,618 ETH Amid Spot ETF Inflows Funstrat’s Tom Lee-backed Ethereum treasury firm Bitmine Immersion
